訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"a084830c2c827926760107d5f130fdf2081ef3e7","tid":1674352,"uid":15337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"我想講，以中共做野咁耐，佢係唔需要放風，放風個d 一定係香港個邊政府既人<br />\n<br />\n你諗下咁耐中共都係直接做，老懵董落台，689 連唔到任 都從來冇放過風，佢只有做定唔做，亦唔需要放風做埋d 19 野。<br />\n<br />\n咁耐以來放風既都係香港政府尤其林鄭放得特別多，例如唔落台啊，101死線啊呢d"},{"pid":"c2004af3a0f17734c5406d2436af0f0926ca1c42","tid":1674352,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae7c751b64475130ca16ebdd945381a23ec7500","tid":1674352,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e7aa6f795f083aacd66b418ac4e80b00c40f2b","tid":1674352,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭：平靜後會有真誠對話<br />\n<br />\n之後用緊急法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624440fe734d416740b9c512963abb6f73c58b90","tid":1674352,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"我只可以講中共未有亡國跡象前，你都唔洗諗普選，仲有亂落去，佢一定拎3萬狗去做回血劍平定香港，狗可換香港不能棄"},{"pid":"eab3bac4edbea82165767a2cfa0737eb0491f275","tid":1674352,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"D風似係林鄭自己放出黎試水溫"},{"pid":"0af60bf4214f64de9e6a9f5bcfb2741db5c9fcd2","tid":1674352,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:05:33.000Z","msg":"你係咪調轉咗次序？你答應咗5大訴求咪無暴亂囉，乜鳩野無暴亂先答應5大訴求，乜邏輯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213b56187941bd9df9ea908169d088aaf941dc33","tid":1674352,"uid":282808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":